'''''Clouseau in 't lang''''' is the name of the concert given by the [[Flanders|Flemish]] band [[Clouseau (band)|Clouseau]] in 2005 at the [[Antwerp]] [[Sportpaleis Merksem]].  The name was inspired by the 6 meter wide, 40 meter long catwalk in the concert hall from which the band played.  This unusual arrangement made it possible for the entire hall to see the band more or less equally.

Video of the concert was made available on a DVD with the same name in February 2006.

